ESSAY: 

Write the definition for each of the following terms in your own words:

The Internet of things (IOT)
Blended learning
Online Advertising
Online photo sharing
Website evaluation
Online citizenship
Net neutrality

The Internet of things: When everyday devices are connected to the internet to make them smart.

Blended learning: Learning both though face to face interaction and on computers via the internet.

Online Advertising: Advertising that appears on websites.

Website evaluation: The concept of being critical of the information you read on the internet to check its validity. 

Online citizenship: The idea of treating people online with respect.

Net neutrality: The debate about whether internet providers should be allowed to make rules that favor some products and servers over others.

-Brian Miller
